oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Carl and Pearl Butler Press Release Cont. (negative)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Butler, Carl; Butler, Pearl; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative, with part of a masking sheet stuck to it, containing a portion of the second page of a biography of Carl and Pearl Butler. The text describes songs written by Carl Butler, when Carl and Pearl started performing together, and Pearl's hobbies.
